{"body": "Yes, it works. See [https://github.com/wycats/thor/blob/master/lib/thor/parser/arguments.rb#L139-142].\r\n\r\nBut in this case the `~/.railsrc` arguments [are added after the arguments you passed to the `rails new` command](https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/master/railties/lib/rails/commands/application.rb#L17). So the `-m` option will take precedence over `--no-template`.\r\n\r\nI personally think this should be inverted and the arguments passed to commands should have precedence over the `~/.railsrc` content.\r\n\r\n@josevalim @wycats WDYT?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/11653380", "created_at": "2012-12-24T02:30:50Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8545#issuecomment-11653380", "updated_at": "2012-12-24T02:30:50Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8545, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f247bd3543c15100a5a7"}, "id": 11653380, "issue_url": "https://api.github.